raw_body: WIJEWARDENE – SEELA R.I.P. – Beloved wife of the late Ray Wijewardene,​ sister of Rohini de Mel and the late Lakshman,​ precious mother of Anoma,​ Roshini and Mandy; much loved grandmother of Rehan,​ Q,​ Anisha and Tisara; loving mother-in-law of Arjun and Suresh. A private funeral took place according to her wishes on 25th November 2023.077703
